<view class="drag-box">
	<view 
		v-for="(item,index) in dataList"
		:key="index"
		:style="{top: item.top +'px',
			height: (itemHeight - 1)+'rpx'}"
		class="drag-item"
		:class="{'drag-active': item.isActive}"
		@longtap="longtap(item)"
		@touchstart="touchstart"
		@touchmove.stop.prevent="touchmove"
		@touchend="touchend(item)">
			<slot :item="item"></slot>
	</view>
</view>
